item.title: CVE-2023-5685|2024-09-18T08:32:45.227Z -- red%20hat -- eap%207.4.14
item.description: A flaw was found in XNIO. The XNIO NotifierState that can cause a Stack Overflow Exception when the chain of notifier states becomes problematically large can lead to uncontrolled resource management and a possible denial of service (DoS).
